      "content": "Sometimes I look in the mirror and I don't even recognize the person looking back. It feels like the version of me that actually had dreams and a future died a long time ago. Now I'm just... going through the motions. Like a ghost or a corpse just walking around. I'm not even really \"here\" anymore.",
