    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I don't know if it's just \"disconnection\" though. It feels more permanent than that. It's like the person who used to care, the person who actually lived, is just... gone. There's no more \"inner self\" to reconnect with. It's just an empty shell doing the work of a person. It feels like I'm just waiting for the rest of me to catch up with what already happened.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
